PN,30301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784679493
OL,3,CUK hotspots for consistent growth in
OL,4,Chome values revealed by property
OL,5,Cwebsite
OL,7,FOnly about one in seven homes across
OL,8,Fthe UK has consistently increased
OL,9,Fannually in value from June 2022
OL,10,Fonwards, according to estimates by a
OL,11,Fproperty website.
OL,13,FZoopla analysed valuations of
OL,14,Findividual homes, starting in June
OL,15,F2021 and ending in June 2026.
OL,17,FIt specifically looked at the month of
OL,18,FJune, analysing whether valuations had
OL,19,Fincreased that month compared with the
OL,20,Fmonth of June the year before.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784679493
OL,3,CUK hotspots for consistent growth in
OL,4,Chome values revealed by property
OL,5,Cwebsite
OL,7,FFor example, covering the first year,
OL,8,FZoopla looked at whether the valuation
OL,9,Fof a home in June 2022 was higher than
OL,10,Fin June 2021.
OL,12,FZoopla estimated that just 14% of UK
OL,13,Fhomes ` equating to just over four
OL,14,Fmillion properties ` had increased in
OL,15,Fvalue annually each June from June
OL,16,F2022 to June 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784679493
OL,3,CUK hotspots for consistent growth in
OL,4,Chome values revealed by property
OL,5,Cwebsite
OL,7,FWhile some homes will not have
OL,8,Fconsistently increased in value each
OL,9,Fyear, Zoopla said its house price
OL,10,Findex indicates the average UK home
OL,11,Fvalue has increased by 15.3% over the
OL,12,Fpast five years, equating to an
OL,13,Faverage of #36,100 per home.
OL,15,FZoopla said that rises in mortgage
OL,16,Frates, affecting borrowers' costs,
OL,17,Fwill have had an impact over the five-
OL,18,Fyear period.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784679493
OL,3,CUK hotspots for consistent growth in
OL,4,Chome values revealed by property
OL,5,Cwebsite
OL,7,FRichard Donnell, executive director at
OL,8,FZoopla, said: "Housing markets across
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland, the North and
OL,10,FScotland have seen homeowners keep
OL,11,Fbuilding equity in their home because
OL,12,Fthe local housing market was less
OL,13,Fexposed to the affordability pressures
OL,14,Fthat higher mortgage rates bring.
OL,16,F"For homeowners, this analysis
OL,17,Fhighlights why you cannot rely on
OL,18,Fnational or regional averages when
OL,19,Fassessing what your home is worth.
OL,26,@pD@OOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784679493
OL,3,CUK hotspots for consistent growth in
OL,4,Chome values revealed by property
OL,5,Cwebsite
OL,7,F"Trends vary by property type and at a
OL,8,Fhyper local level.
OL,10,F"Understanding whether your local area
OL,11,Fhas consistently built equity or
OL,12,Fflatlined is essential information, if
OL,13,Fyou want to understand what you can
OL,14,Fafford to buy next or you are actively
OL,15,Fplanning your next move."
OL,17,FAneisha Beveridge, research director
OL,18,Fat Connells Group, said: "The UK's
OL,19,Fhousing market has become increasingly
OL,20,Ffragmented over the last five years.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUwD@YO]zD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784679493
OL,3,CUK hotspots for consistent growth in
OL,4,Chome values revealed by property
OL,5,Cwebsite
OL,7,F"The strongest performance has
OL,8,Fgenerally come from more affordable
OL,9,Fmarkets across the north of England,
OL,10,FScotland and Northern Ireland, where
OL,11,Flower price points have helped
OL,12,Finsulate buyers from higher mortgage
OL,13,Frates and supported continued demand.
OL,15,F"At the same time, the pandemic
OL,16,Fsparked a surge in demand for larger
OL,17,Fhomes in commutable areas outside
OL,18,FLondon, driving strong price growth
OL,19,Facross much of the south between 2020
OL,20,Fand 2022.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784679493
OL,3,CUK hotspots for consistent growth in
OL,4,Chome values revealed by property
OL,5,Cwebsite
OL,7,F"However, as mortgage rates rose and
OL,8,Fstamp duty incentives were withdrawn,
OL,9,Fthat momentum faded and price growth
OL,10,Fin many of these markets has since
OL,11,Fcome under pressure.
OL,13,F"Despite these headwinds, our research
OL,14,Fshows the middle market is still
OL,15,Fmoving.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784679493
OL,3,CUK hotspots for consistent growth in
OL,4,Chome values revealed by property
OL,5,Cwebsite
OL,7,F"Most buyers and sellers are driven by
OL,8,Flife events rather than short-term
OL,9,Fhouse price movements, and for
OL,10,Fhomeowners who typically move every 10
OL,11,Fto 12 years, modest annual price falls
OL,12,Frarely affect their ability to
OL,13,Ftransact.
OL,15,F"The challenge comes when weak price
OL,16,Fgrowth persists for many years."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784679493
OL,3,CUK hotspots for consistent growth in
OL,4,Chome values revealed by property
OL,5,Cwebsite
OL,7,FCharlotte Harrison, chief executive
OL,8,Fofficer of home financing at Skipton
OL,9,FBuilding Society, said: "Consistent
OL,10,Fhouse price growth can help homeowners
OL,11,Fbuild equity, but equity alone doesn't
OL,12,Fguarantee people can move.
OL,14,F"Our latest Skipton Group home
OL,15,Faffordability index found the gap
OL,16,Fbetween buying affordability and
OL,17,Fliving affordability is the widest
OL,18,Fit's been this decade.
OL,26,@qD@YOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784679493
OL,3,CUK hotspots for consistent growth in
OL,4,Chome values revealed by property
OL,5,Cwebsite
OL,7,F"For many households, the challenge is
OL,8,Fno longer whether their home has risen
OL,9,Fin value, but whether they can afford
OL,10,Fthe higher ongoing costs of their next
OL,11,Fproperty."
OL,13,FShe added: "While sustained house
OL,14,Fprice growth can be positive for
OL,15,Fexisting homeowners, improving access
OL,16,Fto homeownership remains critical if
OL,17,Ffuture generations are to share in
OL,18,Fthose benefits too."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@JO]uD@LOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784679493
OL,3,CUK hotspots for consistent growth in
OL,4,Chome values revealed by property
OL,5,Cwebsite
OL,7,FNathan Emerson, CEO at property
OL,8,Fprofessionals' body Propertymark,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Many purchasers are factoring
OL,10,Fin the long-term cost of homeownership
OL,11,Frather than focusing solely on
OL,12,Fsecuring a property quickly.
OL,14,F"At the same time, sellers who price
OL,15,Ftheir homes realistically continue to
OL,16,Fattract strong interest, demonstrating
OL,17,Fthat demand remains resilient where
OL,18,Fexpectations align with current market
OL,19,Fconditions."
OL,26,@qD@GOUvD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
